query:
INSERT INTO cloud (
        user_id,
        provider,
        cloud_token,
        cloud_key,
        cloud_secret,
        save_token,
        created_at,
        updated_at
        )
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, NOW() at time zone 'utc', NOW() at time zone 'utc')
        RETURNING id;
